{"word":"πρόφασις","slug":"πρόφασις","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>πρόφασις, εως, ἡ</el></b> [<el>προφαίνω</el> (<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:πρό\">πρό</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:φαίνω\">φαίνω</a></el>) ‘bring to light’] ‘appearance or show that hides or conceals’, <b>pretext <a href='B:470 23:14'>Mt 23:14</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a>; <a href='B:480 12:40'>Mk 12:40</a>; <a href='B:490 20:47'>Lk 20:47</a>; <a href='B:510 27:30'>Ac 27:30</a>; <a href='B:570 1:18'>Phil 1:18</a>.</b> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐν\">ἐν</a> προφάσει πλεονεξίας</el> with coverup of greed <b><a href='B:590 2:5'>1 Th 2:5</a>.</b> By <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ ext.\">ext.</a> of the idea of diverting attention, <b>excuse <a href='B:500 15:22'>J 15:22</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:προϋπάρχω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:προφέρω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}